---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="加入我们" description="加入天津大学视觉智能实验室">
  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-tju-red to-red-900 text-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">加入我们</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-red-100">Join ViL - 长期有效</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Positions -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-8">
        <!-- Postdoc -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-tju-red to-red-700 p-6 text-white">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">博士后</h2>
            <p class="text-red-100 mt-1">Postdoctoral Researcher</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 space-y-4">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">研究方向</h3>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                <li>计算机视觉与视频分析</li>
                <li>医学影像处理与理解</li>
                <li>数字文化遗产保护</li>
                <li>机器学习理论与应用</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">应聘条件</h3>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                <li>具有博士学位，年龄一般不超过35周岁</li>
                <li>在计算机视觉、机器学习等相关领域有研究基础</li>
                <li>具有较强的科研能力和团队协作精神</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">薪酬待遇</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">年薪 30-50万（税前），根据资历和能力面议。享受天津大学博士后福利待遇，协助申请博士后公寓。</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">申请材料</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">个人简历、代表性论文、研究计划书</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Research Assistant -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-800 p-6 text-white">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">科研助理</h2>
            <p class="text-blue-100 mt-1">Research Assistant</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 space-y-4">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">岗位职责</h3>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                <li>协助课题组开展科研项目</li>
                <li>参与实验设计与数据分析</li>
                <li>协助管理实验室日常事务</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">应聘条件</h3>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                <li>本科及以上学历，计算机、电子等相关专业</li>
                <li>熟悉Python编程，有深度学习经验者优先</li>
                <li>工作认真负责，具有良好的沟通能力</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">薪酬待遇</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">面议，根据学历和能力提供有竞争力的薪酬</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Graduate Students -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-600 to-green-800 p-6 text-white">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">研究生招生</h2>
            <p class="text-green-100 mt-1">Graduate Students</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 space-y-4">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">招生信息</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">实验室每年招收博士、硕士研究生若干名，欢迎对计算机视觉、机器学习、医学影像处理等方向感兴趣的同学报考。</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">报名方式</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">请通过天津大学研究生招生系统报名，并在个人陈述中注明意向导师。建议提前与导师邮件联系。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Sidebar -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">联系方式</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
            <li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-tju-red" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
              </svg>
              <a href="mailto:wfeng@tju.edu.cn" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-tju-red">wfeng@tju.edu.cn</a>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-tju-red" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-600">天津大学北洋园校区55教学楼</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-tju-red rounded-xl p-6 text-white">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">期待您的加入</h3>
          <p class="text-red-100 text-sm">让我们一起探索视觉智能的无限可能！</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
